    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >One Minute</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入<strong><u>One Minute</u></strong>的疯狂世界！这是一款独特的<strong>Roguelite</strong>游戏，每一秒都至关重要。设计为<strong>快速</strong>、<strong>易上手</strong>且<strong>令人上瘾</strong>，游戏体验完全由鼠标操控。主要特点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong><u>快速多样的迷你游戏</u></strong>：挑战12个迷你游戏，每个仅持续5秒。目标？取得最高分！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏋️ <strong><u>训练模式</u></strong>：在您最喜欢的迷你游戏中磨炼技巧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💻 <strong><u>兼容性与性能</u></strong>：即使是低配置电脑也能流畅运行。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕹️ <strong><u>Roguelite进度系统</u></strong>：通过游戏赚取金币，解锁新的迷你游戏或升级已有的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/908d80f3c9224bda89d0b156f0e73965.poster.avif?t=1740351413\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/908d80f3c9224bda89d0b156f0e73965.webm?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/908d80f3c9224bda89d0b156f0e73965.mp4?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong><u>全球排行榜</u></strong>：与全球玩家一较高下，可按迷你游戏单独排名或总排名。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/3a0b75c409e3ab1b1c65f0dca150b7ea.poster.avif?t=1740351413\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/3a0b75c409e3ab1b1c65f0dca150b7ea.webm?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/3a0b75c409e3ab1b1c65f0dca150b7ea.mp4?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖱️ <strong><u>独特的鼠标光标皮肤</u></strong>：每局结束后获得稀有的鼠标光标皮肤，并可在Steam市场交易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/d07be90e9c676d2d80e045782f19e6bc.poster.avif?t=1740351413\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/d07be90e9c676d2d80e045782f19e6bc.webm?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301260/extras/d07be90e9c676d2d80e045782f19e6bc.mp4?t=1740351413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>准备好迎接一场紧张刺激的体验，每一次点击都至关重要！ 🕒</p>",
